== 事故 ==
澳大利亞衝浪運動員勞理·陶納被聘為主角強尼·猶他的替身，他9月中旬在Teahupo'o進行衝浪特技的拍攝時弄傷了他的下巴<ref>{{cite news|title=Laurie Towner, Aussie stunt double, suffers broken jaw during filming of Point Break 2 in huge Teahupoo surf|url=http://www.news.com.au/sport/sports-life/laurie-towner-aussie-stunt-double-suffers-broken-jaw-during-filming-of-point-break-2-in-huge-teahupoo-surf/story-fno61i58-1227059477116|accessdate=September 28, 2014|publisher=news.com.au|date=September 15, 2014|archive-date=2014-10-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141025050629/http://www.news.com.au/sport/sports-life/laurie-towner-aussie-stunt-double-suffers-broken-jaw-during-filming-of-point-break-2-in-huge-teahupoo-surf/story-fno61i58-1227059477116|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Laurie Towner hospitalised while shooting Point Break 2 at Teahupoo|url=http://stabmag.com/laurie-towner-hospitalised-while-shooting-point-break-2-at-teahupoo/|accessdate=September 28, 2014|publisher=stabmag.com|date=September 14, 2014|archive-date=2015-11-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151125225824/http://stabmag.com/laurie-towner-hospitalised-while-shooting-point-break-2-at-teahupoo/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

== 發行 ==
電影最初原定2015年8月7日上映，但於2014年8月12日，華納兄弟將日期改至2015年7月31日<ref>{{cite news|title=Warner Bros. Dates ‘American Sniper'; Moves ‘Point Break’, ‘Man From U.N.C.L.E’|url=http://deadline.com/2014/08/american-sniper-clint-eastwood-man-from-uncle-point-break-release-dates-818516/|accessdate=August 13, 2014|publisher=deadline.com|date=August 12, 2014|archive-date=2018-06-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180612162356/https://deadline.com/2014/08/american-sniper-clint-eastwood-man-from-uncle-point-break-release-dates-818516/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2015年2月3日，上映日又延後到2015年12月25日，主要是打算與同期的《[[神鬼駭客：史諾登|神鬼駭客：史諾登]]》、《[[神鬼獵人|神鬼獵人]]》、《[[翻轉幸福|翻轉幸福]]》、《[[家有兩個爸|家有兩個爸]]》和《[[震盪效應|震盪效應]]》共同競爭。而《神鬼駭客：史諾登》後來則延了期。

== 反響 ==
=== 評價 ===
[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]評級僅5%<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/point_break_2013/ |title=Point Break (2015) |work=Rotten Tomatoes |accessdate=December 25, 2015 |archive-date=2021-05-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210511121239/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/point_break_2013 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]得分42<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/point-break-2015 |title=Point Break |work=Metacritic |accessdate=December 25, 2015 |archive-date=2020-09-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200909205230/https://www.metacritic.com/movie/point-break-2015 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，普遍獲得負面的評價，主要稱讚視覺上的特技表現，但批評劇情過於薄弱。據[[CinemaScore|CinemaScore]]調查指出，觀眾在A+至F之間平均給了「B」的評價<ref name="CinemaScore">{{cite web |url=http://deadline.com/2015/12/star-wars-the-force-awakens-box-office-pack-as-moviegoers-unwrap-gift-of-choice-1201672136/ |title=Box Office Sleigh Ride: ‘Star Wars’ Soaring, ‘Daddy’s’ Bringing It Home, ‘Hateful Eight’ Selling Out |work=deadline.com |access-date=2015-12-26 |archive-date=2021-02-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210211203328/https://deadline.com/2015/12/star-wars-the-force-awakens-box-office-pack-as-moviegoers-unwrap-gift-of-choice-1201672136/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

=== 票房 ===
中国大陆首週3天收获7600万人民币列第三位，次周收1.2亿居榜首，第三周入账4560万列第三位，最终成绩为2.46亿。香港首週4天获得345万港币居亚军。北市首週以434萬新臺幣居冠。美國首映當天票房為413萬美元，位居第六。

